# Vivado generated cache and build files
**/.cache/
**/*.cache/
**/vivado.jou
**/vivado.log
**/vivado_*.backup.jou
**/vivado_*.backup.log
**/vivado_pid*.str

# IP user files (generated, not source)
**/*.ip_user_files/

# Simulation files
**/*.sim/

# Generated output products
**/*.gen/

# Hardware files (generated)
**/*.hw/

# Vivado project runs (synthesis/implementation results)
**/*.runs/

# Webtalk
**/webtalk*.jou
**/webtalk*.log

# Vivado journal/log backups
**/*.jou
**/*.log

# Modelsim / Questa generated
**/modelsim_lib/
**/work/
**/*.wlf

# Bitstream and other build outputs
**/*.bit
**/*.bin
**/*.mcs
**/*.prm

# IP upgrade log
**/ip_upgrade.log
